                    <p>Role: Solo Game & Level Designer
Engine: Unity 3D | Status: Published on itch.io

Summary:
A psychological first-person horror experience where players explore a haunted house, uncover clues, and survive terrifying events. Built entirely solo using Unity and ChatGPT-assisted scripting.

My Contributions:

Designed the full level layout using modular prefabs, horror lighting, fog, and particles

Used Unity's built-in systems and Inspector to configure environment and gameplay

Implemented a complete first-person controller for player movement

Used ChatGPT to generate and integrate all gameplay scripts (clue pickup, UI prompts, audio logic, cutscene transitions)

Designed clue-based progression and visual feedback through TextMeshPro and UI

Planned end sequence and gameplay flow without direct programming knowledge.</p>
